00:29:51,080 --> 00:29:52,040
Mogu doći po tebe.

361
00:29:52,170 --> 00:29:53,890
Ne treba, ići ću do Kabua.

362
00:30:21,350 --> 00:30:23,560
Ah. Sumida, ideš kući?

363
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:25,740
